'''Richard Chasemore''' is an artist who provided the detailed, technical illustrations for [[Dorling Kindersley|DK Publishing's]] large print publications, including:
*''[[Star Wars: Attack of the Clones Incredible Cross-Sections]]''
*''[[Star Wars: Episode I Incredible Cross-Sections]]''
*''[[Inside the Worlds of Star Wars: Episode I]]''
*''[[Inside the Worlds of Star Wars Trilogy]]''
*''[[Inside the Worlds of Star Wars: Attack of the Clones]]''
*''[[Star Wars: Revenge of the Sith Incredible Cross-Sections]]''
*''[[Star Wars Classic Sticker Book]]''
*[[Star Wars: Complete Locations (2005)|''Star Wars: Complete Locations'']]
*''[[Star Wars: Incredible Cross-Sections]]''
*''[[Star Wars: The Clone Wars: Incredible Vehicles]]''

